    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s got some miles under its belt, of course, but it runs smoothly and still looks great out on the road. It's been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure. This is a perfect pick if you're looking for something dependable that won't break the bank. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Engineered for the purist, this E46 M3 features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six and a tactile 6-speed manual. The mechanical vitals are robust, with a recently serviced high-pressure VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity. Power is delivered through a factory limited-slip differential, while the suspension benefits from Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings for precise cornering. Though it bears the honest patina of a well-loved driver, the compression is optimal and the individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous response. A mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s finest engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
